{"id": "art-13", "label": "Art. 13", "title": "Art. 13: Dreptul la apărare", "slug": "art-13", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 13: Dreptul la ap&#259;rare </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Dreptul la ap&#259;rare este\ngarantat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\n id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\n path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\n <v:formulas>\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 1 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum 0 0 @1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @2 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @0 0 1\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @6 1 2\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @8 21600 0\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\"/>\n  <v:f eqn=\"sum @10 21600 0\"/>\n </v:formulas>\n <v:path o:extrusionok=\"f\" gradientshapeok=\"t\" o:connecttype=\"rect\"/>\n <o:lock v:ext=\"edit\" aspectratio=\"t\"/>\n</v:shapetype><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_286779246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1381\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_286779246\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)P&#259;r&#355;ile au dreptul, în tot cursul procesului,\nde a fi reprezentate sau, dup&#259; caz, asistate în condi&#355;iile legii.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)P&#259;r&#355;ilor li se\nasigur&#259; posibilitatea de a participa la toate fazele de\ndesf&#259;&#351;urare a procesului. Ele pot s&#259; ia\ncuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259; de cuprinsul dosarului, s&#259; propun&#259; probe,\ns&#259; î&#351;i fac&#259; ap&#259;r&#259;ri, s&#259; î&#351;i prezinte\nsus&#355;inerile în scris &#351;i oral &#351;i s&#259; exercite c&#259;ile\nlegale de atac, cu respectarea condi&#355;iilor prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Instan&#355;a poate dispune\nînf&#259;&#355;i&#351;area în persoan&#259; a p&#259;r&#355;ilor, chiar atunci\ncând acestea sunt reprezentate.</span></p>"}